{"tid":2039530,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益]究竟有咩人比得上陳同佳？","createTime":"2020-05-28T05:35:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T10:03:38.000Z","uid":333451,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e593e04c66b4aa457d93a2d584bfd8ad5b5629b9","tid":2039530,"uid":333451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T05:35:44.000Z","msg":"赤砂之蠍，百機操演先可以滅國，佳哥唔洗操控傀儡。<br />\n琦玉要每日死練爛練，佳哥頭髮都冇甩條。<br />\n悟空都要入精神時間房，佳哥直情當監獄就係，眨下眼就出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n對眼得戚過寫輪眼，<br />\n面上帶有靈魂寶石，<br />\n又有管浩鳴作為黑執事。<br />\n令狐冲都要行一行開。<br />\n<br />\n唔洗魔杖 唔洗百寶袋，<br />\n唔洗用劍 唔洗黑旋風。<br />\n<br />\n一頂帽已經變走左香港<br />\n冇人阻止到佢。<br />\n<br />\n我想拜佢為師<br />\n有冇巴打知邊到填form學魔術？"},{"pid":"10638c384b86310854a903647c62d3430ab2673e","tid":2039530,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T05:36:29.000Z","msg":"一戰ge普林西普"},{"pid":"6aded1c09724132a874b74ca91ac75829a653869","tid":2039530,"uid":333451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10638c384b86310854a903647c62d3430ab2673e","tid":2039530,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T05:36:29.000Z","msg":"一戰ge普林西普"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T06:01:31.000Z","msg":"我就覺得佳哥好揪好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一頂帽變走佢"},{"pid":"df63831cab64f75122d9f5762930f22b4eb94458","tid":2039530,"uid":309753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6aded1c09724132a874b74ca91ac75829a653869","tid":2039530,"uid":333451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10638c384b86310854a903647c62d3430ab2673e","tid":2039530,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T05:36:29.000Z","msg":"一戰ge普林西普"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T06:01:31.000Z","msg":"我就覺得佳哥好揪好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一頂帽變走佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T06:09:12.000Z","msg":"真正既帽子戲法"},{"pid":"bee55836d53cdbe872ff1851d805250d14219186","tid":2039530,"uid":171310,"like":1,"dislike":0,